{# ---- 超时强制警告 + fold/workers 建议 ---- #}
{# time_str / steps_remaining / exec_timeout_str 均为 required 字段，不做 if 守卫 #}
{% macro render_timeout_warning(time_str, steps_remaining, exec_timeout_str) %}
## Time and Resource Constraints

- **Total Time Remaining**: {{ time_str }}
- **Total Steps Remaining**: {{ steps_remaining }}
- **Per-Node Execution Timeout**: {{ exec_timeout_str }}
- Your code **MUST** complete within **{{ exec_timeout_str }}** — exceeding this limit will be killed and produce zero score.
- **For image/large datasets (>10k samples)**: Budget time carefully. Prefer fewer folds (3 instead of 5), lower resolution, or smaller model if needed to fit within the timeout. A completed 3-fold run is infinitely better than a timed-out 5-fold run.
{% endmacro %}

